{"tid":1366240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(法國總統) 馬克龍以行動支持「香港示威者」","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:11:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdab8684ad97767969cd982e362d116fae45935","tid":1366240,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yhmetblogspot/photos/a.987044088012396/2544309522285837/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyhmetblogspot%2Fphotos%2Fa.987044088012396%2F2544309522285837%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9xz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=b2729f50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yhmetblogspot/photos/a.987044088012396/2544309522285837/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n作者<br />\n7月20日 00:40 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n〈European Parliament resolution on the situation in Hong Kong〉議案還有另一個玄機，看看這85位議員的名單，佔最多席數的是Renew Europe。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>這個黨團，上個月20號才成立，由ADLE解散再組，口號是「文藝復興」，牽頭人係法國總統馬克龍。<br />\n<br />\n你再睇睇RE的黨團組成，隸屬它的英國政團不是執政保守黨，不是工黨，而是第三大的自由民主黨。</strong><br />\n<br />\n而在上月的歐洲議會選舉，英國得票最多的是脫歐黨，其次是自由民主黨，工黨和保守黨分別第四和第五。<br />\n<br />\n如無意外約翰遜會贏侯俊偉上場，脫歐談判就算不引發提早大選，約翰遜都只會做三年。現實的英國人，選脫歐黨不過是想他們在歐洲議會搞搞震，但講到英國首相，很大機會將押在自由民主黨身上。<br />\n<br />\n香港朋友，認識誰是你的盟友。<br />\n<br />\n作者"},{"pid":"e22e9bfecfef3aed440fb8fe4720f859567f9442","tid":1366240,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/W7vB6rq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7vB6rq.jpg&h=7d5b06ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3adad9cf97e3bb37645fd2217515fff58aa9c5c9","tid":1366240,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850479c7ed680a9bf07b20effe24cef27913609a","tid":1366240,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco